article.description: — Garrett Hicks had a career-high 27 points as Alabama A&M topped Southern 68-58 on Saturday.
article.headline: Hicks scores 27 to carry Alabama A&M past Southern 68-58
article.linkText: Hicks scores 27 to carry Alabama A&M past Southern 68-58
article.story: NORMAL, Ala. -- — Garrett Hicks had a career-high 27 points as Alabama A&M topped Southern 68-58 on Saturday. Jalen Johnson had 19 points for Alabama A&M (4-0, 2-0 Southwestern Athletic Conference). EJ Williams added three blocks. Anjay Cortez had nine rebounds. Harrison Henderson scored a career-high 21 points and had 10 rebounds for the Jaguars (3-5, 3-1). ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
